## Polylang

- `lang` option on `wpFetch` injects `?lang=nl` (or `en`) automatically.
- `src/lib/wordpress/polylang-locale-hrefs.ts` — fetches alternate-language URLs for `<link rel="alternate" hreflang>`.
- `/api/locale-hrefs` route: `GET ?pathname=...` — called client-side by the language switcher.
- `src/lib/i18n/config.ts` — `DEFAULT_LOCALE`, `SUPPORTED_LOCALES` from env.
- `src/lib/i18n/locales.ts` — `Locale` type (`"nl" | "en"`).

---

## Contact Form 7

- Form definitions fetched via `fetchCf7Form(id, lang)` from `fetch-cf7-form.ts`.
- Form submission via server action in `submit-cf7-form.ts`.
- `FormEmbedSection` / `CF7Form` components handle rendering.
- Default form ID from `NEXT_PUBLIC_DEFAULT_CF7_FORM_ID` (also accessible via `getDefaultContactFormId()`).
- `faq_contact_split` sections with `useForm: true` get their form definition from `enrichSections()` in `enrich-sections.ts`.

---

## OMB Form Builder (free demo)

- Headless submit: `POST {WORDPRESS_API_URL}/custom-form-builder/v1/public/forms/{id}/submit` with JSON `{ cfb, cfb_visible_fields, cfb_post_id }` and `Authorization: Bearer` from `getOmbFormBuilderHeadlessSubmitSecret()` (`OMB_FORM_BUILDER_SUBMIT_SECRET` or `CFB_HEADLESS_SUBMIT_SECRET`, must match `CFB_HEADLESS_SUBMIT_SECRET` in WordPress).
- Next proxy: `src/app/api/forms/free-demo/route.ts` + `submit-omb-free-demo-lead.ts`. Field keys inside `cfb` must match the published form’s field ids (see `README.md`).

