## ISR revalidation

`POST /api/revalidate` with body:
```json
{ "secret": "<REVALIDATION_SECRET>", "path": "/nl/over-ons" }
// or
{ "secret": "<REVALIDATION_SECRET>", "tag": "pages" }
```

Both `path` and `tag` are optional; at least one should be provided. Returns 200 on success, 401 on wrong secret, 500 on error.

---

## Menu resolution

Menus are resolved via `fetch-menu.ts`:
1. If `WP_MENU_{LOCATION}_{LANG}` env is set → `GET /wp/v2/menu-items?menus={id}`.
2. Otherwise → public fallback `GET /omb-headless/v1/menu?location={loc}&lang={lang}` (theme-side resolver; no env IDs required).

