## WordPress-related env vars

| Var                               | Purpose                                              |
| --------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------- |
| `WORDPRESS_API_URL`               | WP REST base (e.g. `https://cms.salonora.nl`)        |
| `WORDPRESS_BASE_URL`              | WP home URL (used for image remotePatterns)          |
| `WORDPRESS_APPLICATION_USER`      | Basic auth username                                  |
| `WORDPRESS_APPLICATION_PASSWORD`  | Basic auth password (Application Password)           |
| `REVALIDATION_SECRET`             | ISR revalidation shared secret                       |
| `NEXT_PUBLIC_DEFAULT_CF7_FORM_ID` | Default CF7 form ID for contact forms                |
| `OMB_FORM_BUILDER_SUBMIT_SECRET` / `CFB_HEADLESS_SUBMIT_SECRET` | Bearer for OMB Form Builder headless free-demo submit |
| `WORDPRESS_SERVICE_REST_BASE`     | CPT REST base for services (default: `service`)      |
| `WORDPRESS_TESTIMONIAL_REST_BASE` | CPT REST base for testimonials                       |
| `WORDPRESS_CASE_STUDY_REST_BASE`  | CPT REST base for case studies (default: `case_study`) |
| `HOMEPAGE_SLUG` / `*_NL` / `*_EN`| Slug(s) for the homepage per lang                    |
| `WORDPRESS_BLOG_PAGE_SLUG` / `*_NL` / `*_EN` | Blog archive slug segment (default: `blog`) |
| `WORDPRESS_CASE_STUDY_PAGE_SLUG` / `*_NL` / `*_EN` | Case study archive slug (default: `case-studies`) |
| `WP_MENU_{PRIMARY\|FOOTER\|LEGAL}_{NL\|EN}` | Menu IDs by location and language (optional) |

